  m_Name: L1011_HealthBarNullRef
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  exerciseNumber: 11
  exerciseName: HealthBarNullRef
  exerciseTitle: Health Bar Null Reference
  videoWalkthroughUrl: https://unitycodemonkey.teachable.com/courses/problem-solving/lectures/63458640
  exerciseText: Health Bar error
  hintText: Check transform name
  solutionText: 'Find(); is looking for an object named "Bar" but the actual object
    is named "Bar " with an invisible space at the end therefore the Find(); fails.

    The
    solution is to rename the object to name it exactly "Bar", or a better solution
    is to just not use Find(); and strings at all and just use a SerializeField and
    drag the reference.'
